<br>
__________________________________________________<br>
Mirre is a Weaver, someone who does magic, and her mother has just died in a horrific massacre at the intitution where she (the mother) has been living. <br>
Mirre (though she is a Weaver) lives on the Outside (the normal world) because her parents were banished from the magic community. she joins forces with another Outsider named Simon. as a teenager he had left the protection of the magic community and made a life Outside.<br>
now big bad Evil is on the rise with the help of a Summoner (bad magicians who call up creatures from Between to do their dirty work). and this Summoner is being protected by the Evil from Between. in fact, the only thing that could destroy him is Arthur's sword (Excalibur). only it's been lost for centuries. <br>
Mirre and Simon undertake a quest to find Merlin (still trapped in a rock somewhere) who can lead them into the old magic world Inside to search for the sword and hopefully save the world from destruction. <br>
____________________________________________________<br>
<br>
so, that's the general idea. if you want details you should look at the first chapter which is posted in the writer's forum. any comments or critique is welcomed. or if you have questions, etc, please feel free to ask them. <br>
